{"word":"H4886 - מָשַׁח - mâshach - maw-shakh' - Anoint","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָשַׁח</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>mâshach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>maw-shakh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Anoint"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அபிஷேகஞ்செய், அபிஷேகம் பண்ணு, அபிஷேகம்பெறு, அபிஷேகம்பெற்றவனாயிரு, பூசிக்கொள்ளு, தடவப்படு, பூசப்படு, பூசு, தடவு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to smear, to anoint, to spread a liquid"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to smear"},{"paragraph":"2) to anoint (as consecration)"},{"paragraph":"3) to anoint, to consecrate"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be anointed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>rub</i> with oil, that is, to <i>anoint</i>; by implication to <i>consecrate</i>; also to <i>paint: - </i>anoint, paint."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4473 - מִמְשַׁח - mimshach - mim-shakh'/4473\">H4473</a>, <a href=\"#/H4886 - מָשַׁח - mâshach - maw-shakh'/4886\">H4886</a>, <a href=\"#/H4888 - מִשְׁחָה - mishchâh - meesh-khaw'/4888\">H4888</a>, <a href=\"#/H4897 - מֶשִׁי - meshîy - meh'-shee/4897\">H4897</a>, <a href=\"#/H4898 - מְשֵׁיזַבְאֵל - Mᵉshêyzabʼêl - mesh-ay-zab-ale'/4898\">H4898</a>, <a href=\"#/H4899 - מָשִׁיחַ - mâshîyach - maw-shee'-akh/4899\">H4899</a>"}]}